

---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AmicBridge | Building Trust Between People, Not Institutions">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900 via-blue-950 to-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl bg-white/5 text-slate-100 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-700 p-10 md:p-16 backdrop-blur-md text-center">

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-300 mb-8">
        Building Trust Between People, Not Institutions
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-12">
        AmicBridge is a private community where verified members connect directly —
        lenders, borrowers, and investors working together safely and transparently.
        We don’t handle money — we build verified bridges between people who do.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-slate-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm inline-block px-10 py-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-slate-700">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-2">Private Membership Access</h2>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">
          $100 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">(one-time access fee)</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
          Membership gives you verified access to our private contact network — where trusted
          lenders and borrowers meet directly, with safety and confidentiality ensured.
        </p>

        <a
          href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%20AmicBridge%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20join%20the%20network%20and%20verify%20my%20payment."
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition transform hover:scale-105 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          💬 Contact Us on WhatsApp to Join
        </a>

        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm italic">
          After manual payment verification, you’ll receive your secure private access link.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-slate-300">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-4">Why People Trust AmicBridge</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>🤝 Verified, one-to-one introductions to genuine lenders and borrowers</li>
          <li>🔒 Private and encrypted communication channels</li>
          <li>🌍 A growing network of real, verified members worldwide</li>
          <li>🧩 Simple, transparent access — one fee, lifetime membership</li>
          <li>👥 Dedicated human support every step of the way</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
